'''Helpless Automaton''' is the fifth song on the album [[Business As Usual]] by the popular Australian band [[Men at Work]].  It is the only song on the album written solely by the keyboard/flute/saxophone player [[Greg Ham]], who sings to song.  Helpless Automaton features a catchy beat and melody as well as a guitar solo at the end by guitarist [[Ron Strykert]].  The song was never released as a single.

